# Linter Definition

**Who:** Linter tool (e.g., ArchitectTasksLinterTool)
**What:** Enforces code style, detects code smells, ensures consistency
**When:** On file save, commit, or CI run
**Where:** Used in all or specific projects (document here)
**Why:** To prevent bugs, improve readability, maintain standards, automate review
**How:** Analyzes source code, flags violations, provides feedback
